Ceilings', '- Large Bedrooms', '*Select Homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Reserved Parking', '- 24-Hour Package Lockers with Amazon HUB', '- Easy Freeway Access', '- Credit Cards Accepted', '- Clubhouse Rental Available', '- Covered Parking', '- Business Center', '- Heated Swimming Pool', '- Extensive Landscaping', '- 24-Hour Maintenance', '- Playground', '- Convenient Location', '- 24-Hour Courtesy Patrol', '- Recycling bins located throughout the community', '- Off-Leash Dog Park', '- Resident BBQ Area', '- 24-Hour Online Maintenance Request Submittals', '- 24-Hour Fitness Room', 'Pet Policy', 'Our pet policy allows a maximum of 2 pets per home.', 'The monthly pet charge is $35 per pet and the pet deposit is $500 ($200.00 of this is fully refundable).', 'Driving Directions', 'From I-5 take the 128th St Exit, Head West.', 'Take a right on to Admiralty Way.', 'HighGrove is the first drive way on your right.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'Everett Mukilteo Lynnwood I5 I405 Boeing Microsoft Seattle Airport Everett Community College Highway 99 Edmonds Community College Snohomish County King County Everett Station Townhomes Alderwood Mall Maintenance Courtesy Patrol Pet Friendly Everett Mall Xfinity Arena Puget', 'Sound Naval Station', 'BYsEvbo0zMDs']
